Uses of Class
org.microbean.configuration.cdi.annotation.ConfigurationValue.Literal

  • Packages that use ConfigurationValue.Literal 
    Package Description
    org.microbean.configuration.cdi.annotation
    Provides annotation classes and interfaces for helping to integrate the microBean™ Configuration framework into CDI.

    • Uses of ConfigurationValue.Literal in org.microbean.configuration.cdi.annotation

      Methods in org.microbean.configuration.cdi.annotation that return ConfigurationValue.Literal 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      static ConfigurationValue.Literal ConfigurationValue.Literal.of(String name)
      Returns a new ConfigurationValue.Literal representing a ConfigurationValue instance whose ConfigurationValue.value() method will return the supplied name.
      static ConfigurationValue.Literal ConfigurationValue.Literal.of(String[] names)
      Returns a new ConfigurationValue.Literal representing a ConfigurationValue instance whose ConfigurationValue.value() method will return the supplied names.
      static ConfigurationValue.Literal ConfigurationValue.Literal.of(String[] names, String defaultValue)
      Returns a new ConfigurationValue.Literal representing a ConfigurationValue instance whose ConfigurationValue.value() method will return an array containing only the supplied names and whose ConfigurationValue.defaultValue() method will return the supplied defaultValue.
      static ConfigurationValue.Literal ConfigurationValue.Literal.of(String name, String defaultValue)
      Returns a new ConfigurationValue.Literal representing a ConfigurationValue instance whose ConfigurationValue.value() method will return an array containing only the supplied name and whose ConfigurationValue.defaultValue() method will return the supplied defaultValue.
